[There have been 4 cases in Guinea in the past 21 days, making a cumulative total of 3351 confirmed cases and 2083 deaths. No new cases have been reported in Sierra Leone and Liberia. The complete situation report, including tables and figures, is available at the source URL above. - Mod.LK]

